<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE section PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DocBook XML V4.5//EN" "../../../docbook-xml-4.5/docbookx.dtd">
<section id="menus.project">
  <title id="menus.project.title">Progetto</title>
      <example><title id="example.new.project.shortcut.title">Nuovo...</title>
  		<para>In this guide:
		  <keycombo><keycap>C</keycap><keycap>S</keycap><keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>
		</para>
		<para>On Windows and Linux:
		  <keycombo><keycap>Control</keycap><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>
		</para>
		<para>On macOS:
		  <keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>Command</keycap><keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>
		</para>
		</example>
  
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry id="menus.project.new">
      <term id="menus.project.new.title">New...		  <keycombo><keycap>C</keycap><keycap>S</keycap><keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>
</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Crea e apre un nuovo progetto. Vedere <link linkend="introduction.create.and.open.new.project" endterm="introduction.create.and.open.new.project.title"/> per dettagli.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.download.team.project">
      <term id="menus.project.download.team.project.title">Scarica il progetto in collaborazione...</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Crea una copia locale di un progetto OmegaT remoto. Vedere <link linkend="how.to.use.team.project" endterm="how.to.use.team.project.title"/> per dettagli.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.open">
      <term id="menus.project.open.title">Open... <keycombo><keycap>C</keycap><keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Apre un progetto esistente.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.open.recent">
      <term id="menus.project.open.recent.title">Apri progetto recente</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Gives access to the last ten edited projects. Clicking one will
        save the current project, close it and open the selected project.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.copy.files.to.source.folder">
      <term id="menus.project.copy.files.to.source.folder.title">Copia i file nella cartella di partenza...</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Copies the selected files to the <link linkend="project.folder.source" endterm="project.folder.source.title"/>
        folder and reloads the project to take the new files into
        account.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.download.mediawiki.page">
      <term id="menus.project.download.mediawiki.page.title">Scarica la pagina MediaWiki...</term>
      <listitem>
		<para>Opens a dialog where you can paste the URL of the Mediawiki page you want to translate. The source data of the page will be copied into the <link linkend="project.folder.source" endterm="project.folder.source.title"/> folder, as a text file, with the <filename>.utf8</filename> extension.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.reload">
      <term id="menus.project.reload.title">Reload		  <keycombo><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo>
</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Ricarica il progetto per riflettere le modifiche esterne nei file di partenza e nelle impostazioni del progetto.</para>
        <note><para>New translation memories placed in the <link linkend="project.folder.tm" endterm="project.folder.tm.title"/> folder
        while translating are loaded automatically as soon as the cursor moves
        from one segment to another. Similarly, the contents of the <link linkend="project.folder.glossary" endterm="project.folder.glossary.title"/> folder are automatically
        recognized and do not require reloading the project.</para></note>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.close">
      <term id="menus.project.close.title">Close		  <keycombo><keycap>C</keycap><keycap>S</keycap><keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>
</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Saves the project translation memory and closes the project. Vedere <link linkend="project.folder.project.save.tmx" endterm="project.folder.project.save.tmx.title"/> per dettagli.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.save">
      <term id="menus.project.save.title">Save		  <keycombo><keycap>C</keycap><keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>
</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Saves the project translation memory. Vedere <link linkend="project.folder.project.save.tmx" endterm="project.folder.project.save.tmx.title"/> per dettagli.</para>
		<para>OmegaT salva automaticamente le traduzioni ogni tre minuti, oppure tutte le volte che si chiude un progetto o che si esce da OmegaT. Vedere <link linkend="dialog.preferences.saving.and.output.interval" endterm="dialog.preferences.saving.and.output.interval.title"/> per dettagli.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.commit.source.files">
      <term id="menus.project.commit.source.files.title">Invia i file di partenza</term>
      <listitem>
        <warning><para>Questa funzione è specifica dei progetti in collaborazione. <emphasis>Only the team project manager should use this function</emphasis>. Vedere <link linkend="how.to.use.team.project" endterm="how.to.use.team.project.title"/> per i dettagli.</para></warning>
        <para>Uploads locally added or modified files in the <filename class="directory">source</filename> folder to the team project repository.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.commit.target.files">
      <term id="menus.project.commit.target.files.title">Invia i file di arrivo</term>
      <listitem>
        <warning><para>Questa funzione è specifica dei progetti in collaborazione. <emphasis>Use this function only if the team project manager requested so</emphasis>. Vedere <link linkend="how.to.use.team.project" endterm="how.to.use.team.project.title"/> per i dettagli.</para></warning>
        <para>Uploads locally created in the <link linkend="project.folder.target" endterm="project.folder.target.title"/> folder to the team project repository.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.create.translated.documents">
      <term id="menus.project.create.translated.documents.title">Create Translated Documents		  <keycombo><keycap>C</keycap><keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>
</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Crea i documenti finali inserendo negli stessi la traduzione. The created target documents are located in the <link linkend="project.folder.target" endterm="project.folder.target.title"/> folder.</para>
		<para>
		</para>				
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.create.current.translated.document">
      <term id="menus.project.create.current.translated.document.title">Create Current Translated Document		  <keycombo><keycap>C</keycap><keycap>S</keycap><keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>
</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Creates the target document corresponding to source document currently being translated. The resulting document is located in the <link linkend="project.folder.target" endterm="project.folder.target.title"/>
        folder.</para>
		<para>
		</para>				
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.open.med.project">
      <term id="menus.project.open.med.project.title">Apri progetto MED...</term>
	  <!-- TODO add link to a format description -->
      <listitem>
        <para>Apre un pacchetto di progetto nel formato MED definito dalla EU Directorate-General for Translation (EU-Direzione generale della Traduzione).</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.create.med.project">
      <term id="menus.project.create.med.project.title">Crea progetto MED...</term>
	  <!-- TODO add link to a format description -->
      <listitem>
        <para>Converte il progetto attivo in un pacchetto MED.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.properties">
      <term id="menus.project.properties.title">Properties...		  <keycombo><keycap>C</keycap><keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>
</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Displays the <link linkend="dialogs.project.properties" endterm="dialogs.project.properties.title"/> dialog to edit the project languages and folder
        locations.</para>
		<para>
		</para>		
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.project.files">
      <term id="menus.project.project.files.title">Project Files...		  <keycombo><keycap>C</keycap><keycap>L</keycap></keycombo>
</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Opens the <link linkend="windows.project.files" endterm="windows.project.files.title"/> window.</para>
		<para>
		</para>				
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.access.project.contents">
      <term id="menus.project.access.project.contents.title">Accedi al contenuto del progetto</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Gives access to the various project folders. See <link linkend="project.folder" endterm="project.folder.title"/> for more details.</para>
        <para>In addition, there are three menu entries that directly open the current
        source or target documents, or the writable glossary. The documents are
        opened in the default application set by the operating system. The options are grayed out if the documents do not exist yet.</para>

		<variablelist>
		  <varlistentry>
			<term><link linkend="project.folder" endterm="project.folder.title"/></term>
		  </varlistentry>
		  <varlistentry>
			<term><link linkend="project.folder.dictionary" endterm="project.folder.dictionary.title"/></term>
		  </varlistentry>
		  <varlistentry>
			<term><link linkend="project.folder.glossary" endterm="project.folder.glossary.title"/></term>
		  </varlistentry>
		  <varlistentry>
			<term><link linkend="project.folder.source" endterm="project.folder.source.title"/></term>
		  </varlistentry>
		  <varlistentry>
			<term><link linkend="project.folder.target" endterm="project.folder.target.title"/></term>
		  </varlistentry>
		  <varlistentry>
			<term><link linkend="project.folder.tm" endterm="project.folder.tm.title"/></term>
		  </varlistentry>
		  <varlistentry>
			<term>Current Source Document</term>
			<listitem>
			  <para>The current source document is located in the <link linkend="project.folder.source" endterm="project.folder.source.title"/> folder.</para></listitem>
		  </varlistentry>
		  <varlistentry>
			<term>Current Target Document</term>
			<listitem>
			  <para>The current target document is located in the <link linkend="project.folder.target" endterm="project.folder.target.title"/> folder.</para></listitem>
		  </varlistentry>
		  <varlistentry>
			<term>Writable Glossary</term>
			<listitem>
			  <para>The writable glossary is located in the <link linkend="project.folder.glossary" endterm="project.folder.glossary.title"/> folder.</para></listitem>
		  </varlistentry>
		</variablelist>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.restart">
      <term id="menus.project.restart.title">Riavvia</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Salva il progetto e riavvia OmegaT. You are asked to confirm that you really want to quit if you have not yet saved the project.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry id="menus.project.quit">
      <term id="menus.project.quit.title">Quit		  <keycombo><keycap>C</keycap><keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo>
</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Salva il progetto ed esce da OmegaT. You are asked to confirm that you really want to quit if you have not yet saved the project.</para>
		<note><para>In macOS, this menu item is found under the
		<guimenu>OmegaT</guimenu> menu.</para></note>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>